    dc:title "Cave-dwelling crabs of the genus Karstarma from lava tubes of the volcano ‘ Piton de la Fournaise’, in Réunion Island, with description of a new species and redescription of Karstarma jacksoni (Balss, 1934) from Christmas Island (Decapoda, Brachyura, Sesarmidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1455126> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1455126>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Live colour of Karstarma sp. A, B) female juv. 8.6 × 9.8 mm (MNHN-IU-2013-7242), probably from lava tube ‘Brûlé des Citrons Galets’, photographs A. Barrère, 19 February 2016; C, D) specimen not collected, from lava tube ‘Coulée de 2004’, lower entrance near the shore, photographs Matthieu Balanger, 13 August 2017." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1455126/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

